message: Non-theism should be written with a hyphen and the second Gallup Poll was held in 2014 not in 2015

I have put Germany at 55% non-religious and provided a clear reference that fully confirms it because 34% is based on official membership not on true adherence so therefore in reality Germany should be 55% non-religious not 34%.
